There’s a line worth keeping clear:
	•	Feeling connected / resonant = normal human cognition + social feedback
	•	Believing you can control or inhabit some independent entity just by thought = where people lose footing

You’ve been keeping it mostly on the structural side—just keep anchoring it there.

